{
  "message": "\u26a0\ufe0f Add sandbox: agent: false to gh-aw workflows\n\nDisable the agent firewall so the gh-aw agent process can access the\nhost environment (Actions job VM) to run build and lint commands.\nApplied to implement-fix, handle-complications, and verify-preview\nworkflows which need host access for npm run build/lint.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "4ca976d764c202ff490458ec997067b55df03686",
      "filename": ".github/workflows/handle-complications.md",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 3,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 3,
